{
  "stem": "13063.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we heard because the Poles that had some contact with Jews in the ghetto, they-- they gave us the information in 1943 about the ghetto uprising in-- in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They said, you Jews should be proud that you are fighting back a little bit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] No, we didn't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just-- we had an inkling, I would say, about an uprising in ghetto Warsaw at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was '42, '43, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Study, pray, wash, do some chores-- I mean, chores for the house, chores for the family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Different-- I mean, there were so many things to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After all, I was still a teenager.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tried to meet some friends, but we-- everybody was preoccupied with himself or herself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody was preoccupied.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People living together in such a close-- such close quarters-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] remarkably, remarkably, there was friendship.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was admiration from one-- for one another.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was the will to survive, the will to-- even the will to observe as many [INAUDIBLE], as many commandments as possible.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were young men of Hasidic background who were hiding-- who were hiding in the ghetto, somewhere in-- in-- in cellars, and they were just practicing Judaism.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were studying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were praying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were occupied only with holiness.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Young-- young men-- Hasidim.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I met occasionally some of these, but they were-- see, they were jeopardizing their lives because if the Germans would find out that they are not-- that they are-- what they are doing, they would immediately shot them or transported them away to camps of extermination.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but it was in the neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, as I said, close quarters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody knew-- knew about everybody else.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
